Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.70,0:00:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫涙子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.95,0:00:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會說自己的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是菲布莉妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那菲布莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都行  知道什麼告訴我什麼好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂美琴?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?  會不會是御坂學姐認識的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.48,0:00:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有印象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.09,0:00:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,親戚?  表妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同父異母的妹妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.42,0:00:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的「妹妹」已經夠多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.22,0:00:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難…難道是姐姐大人的孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算怎麼回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都有我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:01:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是御坂美琴  你是怎樣認識我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.93,0:01:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來小孩子是懂的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.81,0:01:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰危險  誰安全
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有絕招
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手指玩偶?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飲料的贈品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.55,0:01:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒中就一直讓我陪著她喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是那麼喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  我是呱太
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  菲布莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.43,0:01:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你告訴我一些事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那封入率二十四分之一的粉色呱太啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.09,0:02:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  別為了一個兩個手指玩偶就大聲嚷嚷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  菲布莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能擅自拿別人的東西吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全把你當安全地點了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖  那個呱太玩偶是美琴姐姐的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖還給她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  是菲布莉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…在走失孩子和失蹤者中沒有她的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:48.96,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(642.667,645.333)}<Antiskill>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼晚了也無法與警備員的負責人取得聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今晚她就由我來看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們瞧她已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:03:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有弟弟  已經習慣照顧小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  能拜託你一晚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家太小了  一個人的話怕照顧不過來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢  初春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  初春
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔舔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔舔?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你  在這兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們開工了唄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子他娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開動咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是牛肉餅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  把眼睛緊緊閉上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼輪到菲布莉咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫我澆水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  會摔倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涙子  你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個調皮小妮子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  初春  快來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初初
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:06:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你背影略顯陰霾哦  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不在乎呢  就是個贈品而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是個手指玩偶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不挺在乎的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎麼會知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會那麼怕我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說姐姐大人喜歡那個幼女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人  你是這個意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已有覺悟  為了姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寶貝…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白井  你在鬼叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過說真的  她怎麼會知道我的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個孩子有點特別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.51,0:08:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道的確很重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧  厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然舔得那麼若無其事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐天  你太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:09:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚跟我說「超好吃的」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果讓我也舔了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是都道歉了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了呢  菲布莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是找不到她的資料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也向失蹤以及走失人口的數據庫提交了信息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過目前還沒有回應
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:39.56,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(778,646)}<Child Error>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說  她或許是棄童
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搬家的事安頓好了  就來向你們打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子真讓人操心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:08.14,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(659,646)}<Child Error>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是棄童嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然已經用了不少方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可還是查不到她的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就只能等設施的人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但願她能去個好一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還分好壞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說有的設施條件環境很差的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能選去處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初春  沒有關於設施評價排行之類的資料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那麼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經和對方確認好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們好像答應接收了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說可以去「明日檜」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在13學區的設施
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經去拜訪過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:10:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一個暖人心脾的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過有一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好接收手續最快也要5天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前就由我來好好照顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…我也幫忙唄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我如是轉達給對方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  菲布莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願意暫時和我們一起生活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和涙子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對呀  還有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初初也是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有黒子?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有美偉?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了  菲布莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.06,0:23:40.82,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs55\3c&H8D92B0&\b0\pos(1181.87,261.466)}{\c&H0938E0&}{\c&H0938E0&\3c&H7D8BB1&}#\N20\N菲\N布\N莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那在學究會之前都能在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:12:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  差不多到商討會場警備的時間了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再來玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次也叫上絆理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了  菲布莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見  衿衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連對春上都那麼友善!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要讓她叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  這裡真的是學究會的會場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  好像沒什麼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學究會與能力無關
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單純是個發表學術研究成果的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺是缺乏幾分華麗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了癡狂的地步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你的樣子格外失望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想像中的是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  就是那種…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有露天攤啊  還有很多活動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都住在那裡通宵準備啊  之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  所以才一起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是那種感覺的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子也不會無聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  這不是御坂同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  你們怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚后光子  你怎麼在這…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫泡浮万彬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:41.30,small,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  湾内她們的學姐要參加學究會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是去幫忙準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是我和泡浮的熟人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可婚后同學她還是自願來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必介意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我出馬  準備工作瞬間就能完成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  御坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是誰的妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  事出有因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚后同學  這位可愛的小妹妹叫菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛剛和她交上朋友了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  請務必也和我做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫婚后光子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉  請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  請多多指教  光子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又交上了一個朋友!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連婚后都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼各位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們就去開會咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們就四下轉轉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.67,small,NTP,0,0,0,,集合地點在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  我查查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這會場真是夠大的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了初春  洗手間在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是在…那我帶你去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涙子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我回來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能乖乖地和美琴姐姐一起等我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們先暫時離開  你把握好機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你們在這等等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  這地方也太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警衛人員要是再多點…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  送貨地點應該是這裡沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按文件上來說是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我們是沒有權簽收的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:15:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是學究會的贊助品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,負責簽收的學生還沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是常在學究會裡獲獎的學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年其他的會場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常獲獎學校好像幾乎都還沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒  我剛才好像看到常獲獎學校的學生走過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到會場了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些貨物也平安送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那發現對象後再聯絡你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉妹妹  你餓不餓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要不要喝飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉妹妹  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那朵花好漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涙子還不回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真心難對付
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:17:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為我挺招小朋友喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  怎能就此氣餒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此  就算再被搶去也在所不惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稀有中的稀有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就靠這個封入率六十分之一的彩虹呱太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉妹妹  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.15,0:17:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打工還真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  可愛的小蘿莉…呃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:17:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呱太碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  我稍微沒盯住就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  應該走不了多遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涙子…初初…黒子…美偉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已發現對象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:18:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衿衣…光子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝天謝地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:55.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她本人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來遇到了這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好沒出什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我沒看好她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉  佐天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也應該道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  菲布莉也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可讓美琴姐姐擔心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要道歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺間感情好了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看她們那麼開心真是再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.14,0:21:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我婚后光子的辛勞總算沒白費
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀  婚后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自賣自誇還真是丟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我真的有幫上忙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是是  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:30.55,small,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對絕對真的啦
