Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能說是僥倖了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那按老規矩表决吧
